text: KHWK may refer to: * KHWK-FM, a radio station (99.3 FM) licensed to serve Rushford, Minnesota, United States * KHWK (AM), a radio station (1380 AM) licensed to serve Winona, Minnesota, United States * KHWK (Nevada), a defunct radio station (92.7 FM) formerly licensed to serve Tonopah, Nevada, United States
title: KHWK
